s of fluid density, fluid to matrix sphere size ratio,\nmatrix porosity and matrix morphology on the self-diffusion coefficient of hard\nsphere fluids are discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 May 2020 17:44:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-26"}
