ma, suggesting $B\\lesssim 2$~mG\nfor an age of 100~yr, and even $B\\lesssim 1$~mG using the age of Cas A, in\nagreement with other estimates.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 May 2020 13:01:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 16 Dec 2020 14:25:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-10"}
