ense MVS setting.\nThe benchmark and the implementation are publicly available at\nhttps://github.com/mjiUST/SurfaceNet-plus.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 May 2020 13:13:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-28"}
