ular and irregular waves.\nSpeed-ups between 1.71 and 4.28 are achieved with the test cases. The wave\nmodels and the interpolation method are released open-source to the public.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 May 2020 13:42:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-26"}
