sform into each other. Our study reveals a mutual feedback\nmechanism between pattern formation and local symmetry breaking in active\nmatter that has interesting consequences for structure formation in biological\nsystems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 May 2020 15:14:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-02"}
